 蘭頓","lifeSummary":"当Wischard Ledet于大约1164年出生在英国英格兰諾薩普頓史爾其皮三 瓦登时，他的父亲Wischard Ledet29岁，母亲Christian Longstone25岁。他于1198年与Margaret Foliot在英国英格兰諾薩普頓史爾其皮三 瓦登结婚。他们至少是1个女儿的父母。他去世于1222年2月4日之前在英国諾薩普頓史爾其皮三 瓦登。"},"hr":{"Abt 1164–Bef 4 February 1222":"oko 1164.–prije 4. veljače 1222.","1164–1222":"1164–1222.","1166–Female":"1166–preminula","1168–1222":"1168–1222.","1199–1271":"1199–1271","1136–1208":"1136–1208.","1140–Female":"1140–preminula","1198":"1198.","1164":"1164","1140":"1140","1271":"1271","Abt 1164":"oko 1164.","1215":"1215","1136":"1136","1168":"1168","1222":"1222.","1199":"1199","1166":"1166","Bef 4 February 1222":"prije 4. veljače 1222.","about 1199":"oko 1199.","1208":"1208.","Chipping Warden, Northamptonshire, England, United Kingdom":"Chipping Warden, Northamptonshire, Engleska, United Kingdom","Chipping Warden, Northamptonshire, England":"Chipping Warden, Northamptonshire, England","West Langton, Leicestershire, England":"West Langton, Leicestershire, England"},"cs":{"Abt 1164–Bef 4 February 1222":"okolo 1164–před 4. února 1222","1164–1222":"1164–1222","1166–Female":"1166–Zesnulá","1168–1222":"1168–1222","1199–1271":"1199–1271","1136–1208":"1136–1208","1140–Female":"1140–Zesnulá","1198":"1198","1164":"1164","1140":"1140","1271":"1271","Abt 1164":"okolo 1164","1215":"1215","1136":"1136","1168":"1168","1222":"1222","1199":"1199","1166":"1166","Bef 4 February 1222":"před 4. února 1222","about 1199":"okolo 1199","1208":"1208","Chipping Warden, Northamptonshire, England, United Kingdom":"Chipping Warden, Northamptonshire, Anglie, United Kingdom","Chipping Warden, Northamptonshire, England":"Chipping Warden, Northamptonshire, Anglie","West Langton, Leicestershire, England":"West Langton, Leicestershire, Anglie"},"da":{"Abt 1164–Bef 4 February 1222":"omkring 1164–før 4. februar 1222","1164–1222":"1164–1222","1166–Female":"1166–Afdød","1168–1222":"1168–1222","1199–1271":"1199–1271","1136–1208":"1136–1208","1140–Female":"1140–Afdød","1198":"1198","1164":"1164","1140":"